          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "- By compiler: the authors used obsolete decay data.",
                "Therefore compiler was forced to include some",
                "corrections:",
                "1.  Cl-34-m was moved to \"independent\" group, because",
                "the isomeric state could not be produced due to Ar-34",
                "decay",
                "2. The authors could not observe isomer state of K-38.",
                "Isomeric transition is absent. K-38 ground state could",
                "not be produced due to Ca-38 decay. Therefore K-38 was",
                "moved to \"independent\" group too.",
                "3. Mn-52-m was moved to \"independent\" group because",
                "production cross section of its progenitor (Fe-52g) is",
                "less than uncertainty of Mn-52-m production cross",
                "section.",
                "4. Similar reasons are base to move V-48 and Co-57",
                "production cross sections to \"independent\" group."
              ]
            }
          ],
